title: "RAI Toolkit: Responsible AI Governance-as-Code"
abstract: "A demonstration framework for AI risk assessment, policy-backed safeguards, and exportable decision records. Translates NIST AI RMF, EU AI Act, ISO/IEC 42001, OWASP LLM Top 10, MITRE ATLAS, and U.S. federal AI policy into executable Python. Includes Microsoft RAIS alignment, transparency note generation, and AI-powered scenario parsing."
